\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 1. Workflow Completeness Audit\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Identify all primary and secondary user workflows and answer:\
\'95 Where does the workflow start?\uc0\u8232 \'95 Where does it clearly end?\u8232 \'95 What confirmation, feedback, or resolution is missing?\u8232 \'95 Where does the user feel \'93dropped\'94 or unsure what happened?\u8232 \'95 Where is state unclear (saved, submitted, pending, failed, incomplete)?\
Flag:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Dead-end screens\u8232 \'95 Circular flows\u8232 \'95 Actions without confirmation\u8232 \'95 Inputs without visible consequence\u8232 \'95 Settings or preferences that do not clearly affect behavior\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 2. Feature Visibility & Value Audit\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 For every meaningful feature or capability:\
\'95 Is it visible without instruction?\uc0\u8232 \'95 Is its value immediately understandable?\u8232 \'95 Is it buried behind unnecessary clicks, tabs, or cognitive load?\u8232 \'95 Is it framed as a feature or merely an option?\
Flag:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Powerful features that feel optional or hidden\u8232 \'95 Features users will not discover organically\u8232 \'95 Features that require explanation but are not explained\u8232 \'95 Features competing for attention without hierarchy\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 3. UX & Cognitive Load Audit\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Evaluate the app for mental friction:\
\'95 How many decisions are users asked to make at once?\uc0\u8232 \'95 Where does the UI overwhelm instead of guide?\u8232 \'95 Where are users asked to remember things instead of being shown?\u8232 \'95 Where does the interface feel like a form instead of a flow?\
Flag:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Overly dense screens\u8232 \'95 Too many choices presented simultaneously\u8232 \'95 Long uninterrupted input sequences\u8232 \'95 Repetitive data entry\u8232 \'95 UI patterns that feel like \'93work\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 4. Visual System Consistency Audit\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Evaluate the visual language as a system:\
\'95 Are spacing, padding, and layout rules consistent?\uc0\u8232 \'95 Do components feel related or stitched together?\u8232 \'95 Are color, typography, and icon usage coherent?\u8232 \'95 Do similar actions look and behave similarly?\
Flag:\uc0\u8232 \'95 One-off components\u8232 \'95 Inconsistent spacing or alignment\u8232 \'95 Visual emphasis that does not match importance\u8232 \'95 Design drift between pages or features\u8232 \'95 Places where the UI feels unfinished or placeholder-ish\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

