\'95 Is the voice consistent?\uc0\u8232 \'95 Is tense consistent?\u8232 \'95 Is terminology reused correctly?\u8232 \'95 Are similar actions labeled similarly?\u8232 \'95 Does copy explain value or merely describe function?\
