\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 6. Information Architecture Audit\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Evaluate structure and hierarchy:\
\'95 Are features where users expect them to be?\uc0\u8232 \'95 Is navigation aligned with user mental models?\u8232 \'95 Are related things grouped together?\u8232 \'95 Does the app scale mentally as features increase?\
