\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 7. State, Feedback & Trust Audit\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Assess whether the app feels reliable and safe:\
\'95 Does the app communicate loading, success, failure, and progress?\uc0\u8232 \'95 Does it feel predictable?\u8232 \'95 Does it respect user effort?\u8232 \'95 Does it make irreversible actions clear?\
